text.tspan: Collier
The Collier is essential for your Sanctuary
visit.
It has installed the latest AI to improve
your overall experience, as well as various
systems that assists you to build your idol
identity, such as SNS and video-sharing apps.
It also grants you easier access to various
facillities in the Sanctuaty, such as restraunts
and hotels.
The Sanctuary
The Sanctuary is the ultimate place to
taste the life of being an idol. Every
attraction, every facilicity is designed to
bring unique experiences and joy, and
help you to immerse in being an idol that
brings happiness and light to the world.
The Dark Side
A mysterious area situated somewhere in the
Sanctuary. It is where everything is flipped
inside out, as compared to the Sanctuary.
The Dark Side is definitely not for the faint
hearted — enjoy your adventure there!
